081    /**
082     * Create a new {@code LipidMapsParserEventHandler}.
083     *
084     * @param knownFunctionalGroups the known functional groups
085     */
086    public LipidMapsParserEventHandler(KnownFunctionalGroups knownFunctionalGroups) {
087        super(knownFunctionalGroups);
088        try {
089            registeredEvents = Map.ofEntries(
090                    entry("lipid_pre_event", this::resetParser),
091                    entry("lipid_post_event", this::buildLipid),
092                    // set adduct events
093                    entry("adduct_info_pre_event", this::newAdduct),
094                    entry("adduct_pre_event", this::addAdduct),
095                    entry("charge_pre_event", this::addCharge),
096                    entry("charge_sign_pre_event", this::addChargeSign),
097                    entry("mediator_pre_event", this::mediatorEvent),
098                    entry("sgl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
099                    entry("species_fa_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
100                    entry("tgl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
101                    entry("dpl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
102                    entry("cl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
103                    entry("dsl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
104                    entry("fa2_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
105                    entry("fa3_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
106                    entry("fa4_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
107                    entry("hg_dg_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
108                    entry("fa_lpl_molecular_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
109                    entry("hg_lbpa_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
110                    entry("fa_no_hg_pre_event", this::pureFa),
111                    entry("hg_sgl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
112                    entry("hg_gl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
113                    entry("hg_cl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
114                    entry("hg_dpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
115                    entry("hg_lpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
116                    entry("hg_threepl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
117                    entry("hg_fourpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
118                    entry("hg_dsl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
119                    entry("hg_cpa_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
120                    entry("ch_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
121                    entry("hg_che_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
122                    entry("mediator_const_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
123                    entry("pk_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
124                    entry("hg_fa_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),

169    @Override
170    protected void resetParser(TreeNode node) {
171        content = null;
172        level = LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE;
173        headGroup = "";
174        lcb = null;
175        adduct = null;
176        faList.clear();
177        currentFa = null;
178        useHeadGroup = false;
179        omitFa = false;
180        dbPosition = 0;
181        dbNumbers = -1;
182        dbCistrans = "";
183        modPos = -1;
184        modNum = 1;
185        modText = "";
186        headgroupDecorators.clear();
187        addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer = false;
188        heavyElement = Optional.empty();
189        heavyNumber = 0;
190        sphingaPure = false;
191        lcbCarbonPreSet = 18;
192        lcbDbPreSet = 0;
193        lcbHydroPreSet.clear();
194        sphingaPrefix = "";
195        sphingaSuffix = "";
196    }
197
198    private void addAcer(TreeNode node) {
199        String head = node.getText();
200        headGroup = "ACer";
201
202        if (!ACER_HEADS.containsKey(head)) {
203            throw new LipidException("ACer head group '" + head + "' unknown");
204        }
205
206        HeadgroupDecorator hgd = new HeadgroupDecorator("decorator_acyl", -1, 1, null, true, knownFunctionalGroups);
207        int acer_num = ACER_HEADS.get(head);
208        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("decorator_acyl", new ArrayList<>());
209        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("decorator_acyl").add(new FattyAcid("FA", acer_num, knownFunctionalGroups));
210        headgroupDecorators.add(hgd);
211
212        if (head.equals("1-O-lignoceroyl-omega-linoleoyloxy") || head.equals("1-O-stearoyl-omega-linoleoyloxy")) {
213            addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer = true;
214        }
215    }
216
217    private void setHeavyElement(TreeNode node) {
218        String nodeHeavyElement = node.getText();
219        switch (nodeHeavyElement) {
220            case "d":
221            case "D":
222                adduct.getHeavyElements().put(Element.H2, 0);
223                heavyElement = Optional.of(Element.H2);
224                break;
225            default:
226                throw new LipidParsingException("Heavy Element '" + heavyElement + "' unknown!");
227        }
228    }
229
230    private void setHeavyNumber(TreeNode node) {
231        if (this.heavyElement.isPresent()) {
232            this.heavyNumber = node.getInt();
233            adduct.getHeavyElements().put(this.heavyElement.get(), node.getInt());
234        } else {
235            throw new LipidParsingException("Trying to parse Heavy Element number, but no Heavy Element is present!");
236        }
237    }
238
239    private void addAdditionalModifier(TreeNode node) {
240        String modifier = node.getText();
241        if (modifier.equals("h")) {
242            FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
243            String fg_name = functional_group.getName();
244            if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fg_name)) {
245                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fg_name, new ArrayList<>());
246            }
247            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fg_name).add(functional_group);
248            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
249        }
250    }
251
252    private void addCarbonPreLen(TreeNode node) {
253        lcbCarbonPreSet = node.getInt();
254    }
255
256    private void sphingaDbSet(TreeNode node) {
257        sphingaSuffix = node.getText();
258
259        if (sphingaSuffix.equals("anine")) {
260            lcbDbPreSet = 0;
261        } else if (sphingaSuffix.equals("osine")) {
262            lcbDbPreSet = 1;
263        } else if (sphingaSuffix.equals("adienine")) {
264            lcbDbPreSet = 2;
265        }
266    }
267
268    private void newSphinga(TreeNode node) {
269        headGroup = "SPB";
270    }
271
272    private void newSphingaPure(TreeNode node) {
273        sphingaPure = true;
274        lcbHydroPreSet.add(knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH"));
275        lcbHydroPreSet.add(knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH"));
276        lcbHydroPreSet.get(0).setPosition(1);
277        lcbHydroPreSet.get(1).setPosition(3);
278        newLcb(node);
279    }
280
281    private void setHydroPreNum(TreeNode node) {
282        lcbHydroPreSet.add(knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH"));
283        lcbHydroPreSet.get(lcbHydroPreSet.size() - 1).setPosition(4);
284        sphingaPrefix = node.getText();
285    }
286
287    private void addPhospho(TreeNode node) {
288        String phosphoSuffix = node.getText();
289        if (phosphoSuffix.equals("1-phosphate")) {
290            headGroup += "P";
291        } else if (phosphoSuffix.equals("1-phosphocholine")) {
292            headGroup = "LSM";
293        }
294        lcbHydroPreSet.remove(0);
295    }

315    private void addDbPosition(TreeNode node) {
316        if (currentFa != null) {
317            currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(dbPosition, dbCistrans);
318
319            if (!dbCistrans.equals("E") && !dbCistrans.equals("Z")) {
320                setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
321            }
322
323        }
324    }

327        addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer = true;
328        setHeadGroupName(node);
329    }

331    private void addGlyco(TreeNode node) {
332        String glyco_name = node.getText();
333        HeadgroupDecorator functional_group = null;
334        try {
335            functional_group = (HeadgroupDecorator) knownFunctionalGroups.get(glyco_name);
336        } catch (Exception e) {
337            throw new LipidParsingException("Carbohydrate '" + glyco_name + "' unknown");
338        }
339
340        functional_group.getElements().put(Element.O, functional_group.getElements().get(Element.O) - 1);
341        headgroupDecorators.add(functional_group);
342    }

382    private void addFunctionalGroup(TreeNode node) {
383        if (!modText.equals("Cp")) {
384            if (FattyAcid.LCB_STATES.contains(currentFa.getLipidFaBondType()) && modText.equals("OH") && currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH") && currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").size() > 0) {
385                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").get(currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").size() - 1).setPosition(modPos);
386            } else {
387                FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get(modText);
388                functional_group.setPosition(modPos);
389                functional_group.setCount(modNum);
390                String fg_name = functional_group.getName();
391                if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fg_name)) {
392                    currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fg_name, new ArrayList<>());
393                }
394                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fg_name).add(functional_group);
395            }
396        } else {
397            currentFa.setNumCarbon(currentFa.getNumCarbon() + 1);
398            Cycle cycle = new Cycle(3, modPos, modPos + 2, knownFunctionalGroups);
399            if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cy")) {
400                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("cy", new ArrayList<>());
401            }
402            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cy").add(cycle);
403        }
404    }
405
406    private void newFa(TreeNode node) {
407        dbNumbers = -1;
408        currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", knownFunctionalGroups);
409    }
410
411    private void newLcb(TreeNode node) {
412        lcb = new FattyAcid("LCB", knownFunctionalGroups);
413        lcb.setType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR);
414        currentFa = lcb;
415    }
416
417    private void cleanLcb(TreeNode node) {
418        if (sphingaPure) {
419            lcb.setNumCarbon(lcbCarbonPreSet);
420            lcb.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(lcbDbPreSet);
421            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>());
422            for (FunctionalGroup fg : lcbHydroPreSet) {
423                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(fg);
424            }
425        }
426
427        if (!sphingaSuffix.equals("")) {
428            if ((sphingaSuffix.equals("anine") && lcb.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() != 0)
429                    || (sphingaSuffix.equals("osine") && lcb.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() != 1)
430                    || (sphingaSuffix.equals("adienine") && lcb.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() != 2)) {
431                throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with head group description");
432            }
433        }
434
435        if (sphingaPrefix.equals("Phyto") && !sphingaPure) {
436            HashSet<Integer> posHydro = new HashSet<Integer>();
437            for (FunctionalGroup fg : lcb.getFunctionalGroups().get("OH")) {
438                posHydro.add(fg.getPosition());
439            }
440            if (lcb.getFunctionalGroups().isEmpty() || !lcb.getFunctionalGroups().containsKey("OH") || !posHydro.contains(4)) {
441                throw new LipidException("hydroxyl count does not match with head group description");
442            }
443        }
444
445        if (dbNumbers > -1 && dbNumbers != currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds()) {
446            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
447        }
448        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
449            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
450        }
451        if (currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
452            for (FunctionalGroup fg : currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH")) {
453                if (fg.getPosition() < 1) {
454                    setStructuralSubspeciesLevel(node);
455                    break;
456                }
457            }
458        }
459        currentFa = null;
460    }
461
462    private void appendFa(TreeNode node) {
463        if (dbNumbers > -1 && dbNumbers != currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds()) {
464            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
465        }
466        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
467            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
468        }
469
470        if (currentFa.getNumCarbon() == 0) {
471            omitFa = true;
472        }
473        faList.add(currentFa);
474        currentFa = null;
475    }
476
477    private void addEther(TreeNode node) {
478        String ether = node.getText();
479        if (ether.equals("O-") || ether.equals("e")) {
480            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMANYL);
481        } else if (ether.equals("P-") || ether.equals("p")) {
482            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMENYL);
483        }
484    }
485
486    private void addHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
487        int num_h = node.getInt();
488
489        if (spRegularLcb()) {
490            num_h -= 1;
491        }
492
493        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
494        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
495        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
496            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
497        }
498        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
499    }
500
501    private void addDiHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
502        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
503            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
504        }
505
506        FunctionalGroup functional_group_p3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
507        functional_group_p3.setPosition(3);
508        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_p3);
509
510        if (!spRegularLcb()) {
511            FunctionalGroup functional_group_p1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
512            functional_group_p1.setPosition(1);
513            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_p1);
514        }
515    }
516
517    private void addHydroxylLcb(TreeNode node) {
518        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
519            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
520        }
521
522        String hydroxyl = node.getText();
523        if (hydroxyl.equals("m")) {
524            FunctionalGroup functional_group_p3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
525            functional_group_p3.setPosition(3);
526            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_p3);
527
528        } else if (hydroxyl.equals("d")) {
529            if (!spRegularLcb()) {
530                FunctionalGroup functional_group_p1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
531                functional_group_p1.setPosition(1);
532                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_p1);
533            }
534
535            FunctionalGroup functional_group_p3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
536            functional_group_p3.setPosition(3);
537            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_p3);
538
539        } else if (hydroxyl.equals("t")) {
540            if (!spRegularLcb()) {
541                FunctionalGroup functional_group_p1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
542                functional_group_p1.setPosition(1);
543                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_p1);
544            }
545            FunctionalGroup functional_group_p3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
546            functional_group_p3.setPosition(3);
547            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_p3);
548
549            FunctionalGroup functional_group_t = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
550            functional_group_t.setPosition(4);
551            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group_t);
552
553        }
554    }
555
556    private void addDoubleBonds(TreeNode node) {
557        currentFa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() + node.getInt());
558    }
559
560    private void addCarbon(TreeNode node) {
561        currentFa.setNumCarbon(node.getInt());
562    }
563
564    private void buildLipid(TreeNode node) {
565        if (omitFa && HEAD_GROUP_EXCEPTIONS.contains(headGroup)) {
566            headGroup = "L" + headGroup;
567        }
568
569        if (lcb != null) {
570            faList.add(0, lcb);
571        }
572
573        if (addOmegaLinoleoyloxyCer) {
574            if (faList.size() != 2) {
575                throw new ConstraintViolationException("omega-linoleoyloxy-Cer with a different combination to one long chain base and one fatty acyl chain unknown");
576            }
577            Map<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fgroups = faList.get(faList.size() - 1).getFunctionalGroupsInternal();
578            if (!fgroups.containsKey("acyl")) {
579                fgroups.put("acyl", new ArrayList<>());
580            }
581
582            DoubleBonds db = new DoubleBonds(2);
583            db.getDoubleBondPositions().put(9, "Z");
584            db.getDoubleBondPositions().put(12, "Z");
585            faList.get(faList.size() - 1).getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("acyl").add(new FattyAcid("FA", 18, db));
586            headGroup = "Cer";
587        }
588
589        Headgroup headgroup = prepareHeadgroupAndChecks();
590        content = new LipidAdduct(assembleLipid(headgroup), adduct);
591    }
592
593    private void newAdduct(TreeNode node) {
594        if (adduct == null) {
595            adduct = new Adduct("", "");
596        }
597    }
598
599    private void addAdduct(TreeNode node) {
600        adduct.setAdductString(node.getText());
601    }
602
603    private void addCharge(TreeNode node) {
604        adduct.setCharge(Integer.valueOf(node.getText()));
605    }
606
607    private void addChargeSign(TreeNode node) {
608        String sign = node.getText();
609        if (sign.equals("+")) {
610            adduct.setChargeSign(1);
611        } else if (sign.equals("-")) {
612            adduct.setChargeSign(-1);
613        }
614        if (adduct.getCharge() == 0) {
615            adduct.setCharge(1);
616        }
617    }
618}
